{"tid":1113192,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"理性討論，究竟曼城欠缺啲咩","createTime":"2019-04-17T20:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T07:57:41.000Z","uid":137500,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"e887a649171c3033b46bc4e635f0fa27ac096826","tid":1113192,"uid":137500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T20:57:41.000Z","msg":"哥帥黎之前最好成績都係4強<br />\n當嗰時皇巴拜盛世同英超積弱多年<br />\n但哥帥入主後球風幾咁霸道<br />\n破記錄攞英超<br />\n但就連續兩年8強止步<br />\n仲要輸比聯賽對手<br />\n究竟係冇經驗，冇實力，定係冇運呢"},{"pid":"6801adce9ec499e1b190e3a065839ea828bf6f93","tid":1113192,"uid":88763,"like":107,"dislike":0,"score":107,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T20:58:39.000Z","msg":"歐聯冠軍"},{"pid":"849585d0b4b4ca3fd211c7856076b20359e8cf06","tid":1113192,"uid":170772,"like":38,"dislike":4,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T20:58:53.000Z","msg":"冇運"},{"pid":"67a3a69d08b2926dea5154c95e5e4f194362e128","tid":1113192,"uid":208153,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T20:59:08.000Z","msg":"最後幾分鐘仲係到9猜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eadd45d1ade749736216d6146893b8f4516525f","tid":1113192,"uid":6577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T20:59:18.000Z","msg":"運lo屌你"},{"pid":"90e0b612a532fd1af4c98bc3ec466236f2e56330","tid":1113192,"uid":25494,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T20:59:44.000Z","msg":"後防廢到，set波比兒子射<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a676e7a7733f348d630ceda475b57c761b8457f","tid":1113192,"uid":59491,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T20:59:47.000Z","msg":"冇美斯"},{"pid":"fa369db39c9617bf7d627d69b0fa709eece693a1","tid":1113192,"uid":193072,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"0eadd45d1ade749736216d6146893b8f4516525f","tid":1113192,"uid":6577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T20:59:18.000Z","msg":"運lo屌你"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-